description.narrative: Output 1.1. Parents have developed skills related to the comprehensive development of their children from 0 to 6 years of age in the selected municipalities., which contributes to Early Childhood Development, Early Childhood Development (Covid), Economic And Social Policy General, Maternal And Newborn Health. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Evaluations, Research And Data, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Strategies to address cross-cutting issues related to child rights are developed and applied.
